        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3412834720" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6691947484747210223">9/10<br/>A slightly-altered version of the Arthurian legend, focusing on Merlin and his “education” by artifacts left behind on earth by space-faring visitors from other worlds/universes. Full disclosure—I love most anything related to Arthurian lore, and this was a thoroughly enjoyable read. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4766.Andre_Norton' title='Andre Norton' rel='nofollow noopener'>Andre Norton</a> is a master storyteller whose science fiction and fantasy books I have read and enjoyed throughout my life. How I missed this one, I don’t know, but I’m glad I happened to find and read it now.</span>
  <span id="freeText6691947484747210223" style="display:none">9/10<br />A slightly-altered version of the Arthurian legend, focusing on Merlin and his “education” by artifacts left behind on earth by space-faring visitors from other worlds/universes. Full disclosure—I love most anything related to Arthurian lore, and this was a thoroughly enjoyable read. <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4766.Andre_Norton" title="Andre Norton" rel="nofollow noopener">Andre Norton</a> is a master storyteller whose science fiction and fantasy books I have read and enjoyed throughout my life. How I missed this one, I don’t know, but I’m glad I happened to find and read it now.</span>
