<div class='carouselRow' style='width: 3600px'>
<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_5048585'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5048585-humanity-prime"><img alt="Humanity Prime" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1223873637l/5048585._SY160_.jpg" />
